The paper discusses machine learning techniques for feature selection in the context of big data, which is a common topic in the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also focuses on linear ordinal regression, which is a specific type of machine learning problem that falls under the subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of feature selection techniques in the context of image analysis (cs.CV) and statistical analysis (cs.ST) is also mentioned. Finally, the paper discusses the extension of the framework to privileged information, which is a topic in natural language processing (cs.CL).
